title: AS220 Food
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. AS220's Foo(d) works with 44 local farmers and vendors. Provides positions for youth involved in the Broad Street Studio program and/or the RI Training School's culinary arts program. All profits go to supporting AS220's unjuried, uncensored, all ages gallery spaces, performance space and other not-for-profit ventures in the arts.
